=head2 Installation

Follow the Torrus installation guide for the main software installation.

Install Perl modules from CPAN:

  perl -MCPAN -e 'install Spectrum::CLI'

Unpack the plugin distribution package in some directory:

  gzip -dc tp-spectrum-1.X.tar.gz | tar xvf -

Then run the Torrus plugin installation utility, pointing to the
unpacked plugin directory. Specify the Spectrum home directory if it's
different from "/home/spectrum":

  specroot=/usr/Spectrum torrus install_plugin tp-spectrum-1.X


